) \u2212V (x)\n\n\u2261\n\ndL \u00d7 W\n\n(39.8)\n\nwhich is a rectangle of width dL and height \u2212V0.", "embedding": [-0.024562716, 0.0024961142, 0.04332248, 0.000179698, -0.0039268024, -0.012905552, -0.020768188, 0.011493169, -0.06600992, 0.085569635, 0.038898867, 0.018857142, -0.009218375, -0.040966723, -0.04652133, 0.04051277, -0.023062242, 0.001193563, -0.05842462, 0.028519586, 0.020976635, 0.009289406, -0.06274746, -0.017551051, -0.03773475, 0.03155043, 0.019249963, 0.017674314, 0.055527624, 0.047441375, 0.028970724, -0.007989112, 0.010732316, -0.025100376, -0.0018393386, 0.023340479, -0.0040036365, -0.037152387, 0.030703772, -0.029219875, 0.055519786, -0.03177051, 0.0011793899, -0.038653698, -0.019851072, -0.011123797, -0.00901629, 0.01710403, -0.04225472, -0.060399, -0.011633725, -0.015209769, 0.020638488, -0.043684408, -0.020372814, 0.0004864122, -0.019994158, 0.018307304, 0.0023908352, 0.010681664, 0.038914856, -0.0013310281, 0.036893327, -0.016552689, 0.014268834, 0.041622408, -0.0044395225, 0.03620937, 0.0153336115, -0.02289225, -0.016733717, -0.02697024, -0.008037163, -0.011630633, -0.033599406, 0.03856475, -0.014301041, -0.0017968895, -0.06931542, 0.0090786265, 0.025536338, -0.015810005, -0.01615816, 0.02101245, -0.00731725, -0.007348998, 0.006410304, 0.015038038, -0.012009812, 0.0015815056, 0.014793059, 0.06910341, -0.008392327, 0.00016865756, -0.021829743, 0.04084136, 0.008327796, 0.045273006, 0.043264415, -0.0066091507, -0.001502049, 0.037568234, -0.0012032205, 0.024160324, -0.058875773, 0.02385938, -0.012092324, 0.048820417, 0.013539393, -0.05418976, -0.0041210484, -0.033185437, 0.037674867, 0.04797595, 0.006837599, 0.023287792, -0.0015207408, -0.025245115, -0.022201275, -0.037374403, 0.038654376, 0.028429225, 0.025262516, 0.02848981, 0.018336771, -0.0133828595, 0.032521017, 0.01715134, -0.038953032, -0.02296316, 0.0061982255, -0.008327077, -0.02105229, 0.014952803, -0.019208673, 0.008110158, -0.02205565, 0.031883955, -0.008411287, 0.005266547, 